        <p style="margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 18px;"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(84, 141, 212);">清境简介：</span></strong></span></p>
<p style="margin: 5px 0"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px;">具有<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;">“</span>小瑞士<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;">”</span>之称的清境农场位于南投县境内，它成立于<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;">1961</span>年<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;">2</span>月<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;">20</span>日，面积约<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;">360</span>公顷。它是中横公路雾社支线往合欢山的必经之地。<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;">1965</span>年，当时的<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;">“</span>行政院长<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;">”</span>蒋经国感于此处<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;">“</span>清新空气任君取，境地幽雅是仙居<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;">”</span>。于是将原名的<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;">“</span>见晴农场<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;">”</span>改为<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;">“</span>清境农场<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;">”</span>。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 5px 0"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px;"> <img src="http://7xotew.com1.z0.glb.clouddn.com/article-145-0.jpg" title="台湾清境农场旅游攻略_图片_0" width="328" height="220" border="0" style="width: 328px; height: 220px;" alt="台湾清境农场旅游攻略_图片_0"></span></p>
<p style="margin: 5px 0"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px;">清境农场清新、自然且静谧，温和的气候加上丰沛的雨量，使得此地成为经营牧场、种植温带蔬果与花卉的好地方。延绵起伏的山笼罩于淡淡雾气中，欧式建筑的住宿此起彼伏，羊群游荡绿草地，确实跳脱传统景区别具一格。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 5px 0"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px;"> <img src="http://7xotew.com1.z0.glb.clouddn.com/article-145-1.jpg" title="台湾清境农场旅游攻略_图片_1" width="509" height="368" border="0" style="width: 509px; height: 368px;" alt="台湾清境农场旅游攻略_图片_1"></span></p>
<p style="margin: 5px 0"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px;">春季到清境农场，能看到一片欣欣向荣的桃花、梨花、苹果花陆续绽放。<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;">4</span>月全月采收春茶，牧羊区毛地黄盛开，一片奼紫嫣红。<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;">5</span>月为牧区野菊花及合欢山高山杜鹃盛开季。除了春、夏景致不同之外，秋、冬的清境又有一番不同风情。<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;">10</span>月左右的清境农场可以赏枫<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;">,</span>一片片落枫散落<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;">,</span>踩下去沙沙作响浪漫极了。<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;"> </span></span></p>
<p style="margin: 5px 0"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px;"> </span></p>
<p style="margin: 5px 0"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px;"></span></p>
