<p style="margin: 5px 0"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;">※</span>无论由北、中、南各地搭乘公交车，都须至埔里下车，换乘南投客运<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;">(</span>往翠峰、松岗方向<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;">)</span>至清境<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;">(</span>农场<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;">)</span>。<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;"><br>1.</span>由台北可搭国光客运至埔里，换乘南投客运至清境。<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;"><br>2.</span>由台中可搭乘南投客运或全航客运至埔里<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;">(</span>终点站<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;">)</span>，换乘南投客运至清境。<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;"><br>3.</span>由高雄可搭总逹客运至埔里，换乘南投客运至清境。<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;"> </span></span></p>
